spec_data.Name: python3-wand
spec_data.Description:
Wand is a ctypes-based simple ImageMagick binding for Python. It doesn't cover
all functionalities of MagickWand API currently.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 05:14:20 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Ctypes-based simple MagickWand API binding for Python
